# Python Conventions

- Python 3.11 (pyenv)
- Package lives in `src/fantasy_draft_ai/`
- Scripts in `scripts/` are runnable entry points
- Tests in `tests/` with pytest
- Use type hints for function signatures
- Load config from `.env` via `python-dotenv`
